ORLANDO BROWN: Honestly coming to the game I didn't know how big of a deal it was.  I wasn't a kid that grew up watching college football, so I looked at the Rose Bowl as any other bowl.  I understood it was prestigious, but I haven't gotten into college football until I started getting recruited in high school.  After being here for a few days and realizing how big it is, man, I'm excited.
